> http://thread.gmane.org/gmane.comp.gnu.libtasn1.general/54
> 
> Red Hat bug:
> https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=804920
> 
> Thanks and kind regards,

Please use CVE-2012-1569 for this issue.

